observer
Class FSAGraphMessage

java.lang.Object
  observer.FSAGraphMessage

public class FSAGraphMessage
extends Object

Message sent from FSAGraph to classes that implement FSAGraphSubscriber i.e. that subscribe to change notifications from FSAGraph.

Author:
Helen Bretzke

Constructor Detail

FSAGraphMessage

public FSAGraphMessage(int eventType,
                       int elementType,
                       long elementId,
                       Rectangle2D location,
                       FSAGraph source)
Creates a change notification message for FSMGraph to pass to FSMGraphSubscribers.

Parameters:
eventType - ADD, REMOVE, or MODIFY
elementType - NODE, EDGE, LABEL or SELECTION
elementId - the unique id (by type) of the element
location - area in the display where the event occurred
source - message sender

elementId - the unique id (by type) of the element

source - message sender
message - a description of the event fired
